Extremely fun open world third-person shooter set in the fictional US city of Stilwater. Even in 2025 it is still very entertaining and totally worth playing if you are not opposed to mediocre visuals and some jankiness. Unfortunately it is not all sunshine and roses and if you plan on checking it out you will need to install some mods do to outrageous PC port.

Pros:
- Great writing;
- Cool characters;
- Fun and varied missions;
- Awesome voice acting;
- Great controls;
- Very humorous;
- Good arsenal;
- Great attention to details;
- Lots of customization;
- Fun combat;
- Awesome soundtrack;
- Great sandbox with lots of fun activities;

Cons:
- Terrible optimization without mods;
- Visuals age poorly;
